"NY'S BASH IN YK'S STYLE
Did you know, I injured my knee ACL tear in 2016 and it took me almost 6 months to recover but that did not stop my fitness journey as I was more focused on rehabilitation and bcoz of that you know what I can do now!!

So here I am sharing one of my favourite super fun routine!

👉🏼How to do the workout:
• 3-5 Rounds
• No rest in between exercises
• 60 seconds rest after each round

1️⃣ Db Lateral Squat Walk to Curtsy	
M: Db Lateral Squat Walk

2️⃣ Double Arm Row to Upright Row	
M: Bentover Row to Upright Row

3️⃣ Db Front Squat + Cross Butt Kick	
M: Cross Butt Kick

4️⃣ Double Elbow to Knee Crunch	
M: Alt Knee Double Crunch

5️⃣ In and out Burpee	
M: Modified Burpee + Side Tap

💥 Don’t forget to LIKE, SAVE & SHARE if you enjoyed the workout!
